Package piano

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Key
    This class sets properties of a Piano's Key object.
    KeyStrokes
    Records the keys pressed on the piano and the timestamp they were pressed
    Note
    A class that should be used in GamePanel when a key is pressed.
    Piano
    This class draws the piano and initializes the keys
    Recorder
    Represents the recorder class that records the sounds that the Keys play
    Sheet
    Represents the sheet music to be transcribed
    Sound
    Creates/represents the sound which each of the Keys will play
